  "title": "QC Inspector",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Medical Devices Manufacturing Company</strong></li><li><strong>Salary $2500 - $3500 + Allowances + OT + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Boon Lay</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 4 days, 12 Hours Rotating Shift (9am/pm to 9pm/am)</strong></li><li><strong>TRAINING PROVIDED</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Perform quality control inspections using pin gauge, Vison Measurement (VMS) machine, measuring tape etc for dimension measurement, and product functional test such as tensile measurement in accordance with quality inspection standards</strong></li><li><strong>Maintain accurate quality records and retain sample collections in compliance with Good Documentation Practice (GDP) requirements</strong></li><li><strong>Promptly report any product abnormalities and initiate Non-Conformance Report (NCR) when quality issue are identified</strong></li><li>Support supervisor in investigating customer complaints, quality issues, and implementing corrective actions</li><li>Maintain daily 5S housekeeping in the assigned area daily. Ensure safety regulations are being observed at the workplace</li><li>Assist the superior to complete other tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Preferably at least 1 year of QC work background, familiar with 7 QC tools</li><li>Blueprint reading capabilities, and ability to use measuring devices like gauges, meters, calipers</li><li><strong>Training will be provided for candidate without or with lesser experiences</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
